        <li class = "list-group-item">A police bust at the neighboring bar, Hall of Valhalla, turned into a firefight. Neighbors trade rumors of the lingering presence of the vengeful dead.</li>
        <li class = "list-group-item">A drug dealer left a considerable stash of money buried at the site before she was imprisoned. Only her closest family members are aware of the money.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="text-center">
  <button type="button" id="generate-btn" class="btn btn-lg">
